    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "I get this issue when i run it in jenkins CICD pipeline. When ran in intelij, it works perfectly fine. We were running the project with java version 1.8, changed it to 1.11 in the sourceCompatibility in the build.gradle file. Any solution for CICD pipeline since below answers seems on the intelij side"
