    "body" : "<p>This is what worked for me (Intellij Idea 2018.1.2):</p>\n\n<p>1) Navigate to: File -> Settings -> Build, Execution, Deployment -> Build Tools -> Gradle</p>\n\n<p>2) Gradle JVM: change to version 1.8</p>\n\n<p>3) Re-run the gradle task</p>\n"
