    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The following worked for me:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the top right corner of IntelliJ -> click the icon</li>\n<li>In the Project Structure window -> Select project -> In the Project SDK, choose the correct version -> Click Apply -> Click Okay </li>\n</ol>\n"
