    "body" : "<p>For IntelliJ 2019, JDK 13 and gRPC:</p>\n\n<p>Intellij IDEA -> Preferences -> Build, Execution, Deployment -> Build Tools -> Gradle -> Gradle JVM</p>\n\n<p>and <strong>Select correct version</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>you might also have to adding below line in your build.gradle <strong>dependencies</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>compileOnly group: 'javax.annotation', name: 'javax.annotation-api', version: '1.3.2'\n</code></pre>\n"
