  "body" : "<p>I am trying to import Gradle project in Intellij Idea with local Gradle distrib and getting stacktrace with the following message: <code>Could not target platform: 'Java SE 8' using tool chain: 'JDK 7 (1.7)'</code>.\nCould anyone explain please what could be the reason? </p>\n"
